                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "Most impurities bead and slide off a bacallia\u2019s dense wool, leaving it gleamingly clean. This grants the bacallia a +2 racial bonus on saving throws against contact poisons and effects that would entangle it. It also gains a +1 bonus to its touch AC. "
